  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/57f106db99c51c5d735f264b72706c58.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span>Create and sell games, gain fame and wealth, research new technologies, hire employees, upgrade your office, manage taxes and salaries, take loans if needed, and compete with 5000 companies. Experience the thrill of running your own studio in Game Builder Tycoon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/cee05757b1de206018f6d4fe6a750ea5.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/cee05757b1de206018f6d4fe6a750ea5.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/29359ea3170158f0f5aa50d939e400eb.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span>Design standout games by selecting key elements like art, features, quests, dialogue, music, level, and world design. Assign tasks to characters, choose the genre, theme, platform, game size, art style, viewpoint, and features. Launch your game in the market and create sequels. Imagine a platformer game set in a sci-fi world with 2D-pixel art and multiplayer options. The possibilities for customization are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/5017c81551ec03b8c42a378c5d2180f1.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/5017c81551ec03b8c42a378c5d2180f1.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/9eae8fc2cd0e7aef4aa4b9c700cd5671.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span>Choose your character and define their role—be it as a coder or an artist. Each character has three attributes: IQ, creativity, and insight, which affect six skills: tech, art, writing, design, music, and marketing. Create a unique character that fits your vision. As you progress, hire more employees and continuously train yourself and your team in various ways to stay ahead in the competitive market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/dbb3e3bd0440d075d9fa7f74ec690039.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/dbb3e3bd0440d075d9fa7f74ec690039.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/61a91b8d08d52e53c9fcaebaddccb4ad.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/61a91b8d08d52e53c9fcaebaddccb4ad.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/972a607d21e925b87c7da721eecdbc4e.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span>As your game progresses, research and unlock new elements. Discover new genres like survival or simulation, themes like zombies or pirates, devices like consoles or mobile, game sizes, art styles like semi-realistic or stylized, features like localization or tutorials, viewpoints like isometric or third-person, and marketing strategies like free demos or media advertisements. With over 60 things to unlock, the possibilities are endless to create your next hit games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/dcb476846c5d7d22fee0f4dc5f047551.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/dcb476846c5d7d22fee0f4dc5f047551.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/ad2340b1d866d02b122f485bbb196c87.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/f3b8470c75e57c3a80ddc87914d121e2.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/f3b8470c75e57c3a80ddc87914d121e2.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Want to create larger games? Earn enough money to upgrade your office and hire new employees, expanding your team's capabilities to create bigger and better games than ever before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/a210bf886cab84948840deeb055a57e5.avif?t=1745482095\" width=576 height=65 /></span>Feeling unmotivated? Don't worry, you're competing with 5000 other companies. They are smart and hardworking, just like your team. Create better games and use effective marketing tactics to earn more and stay ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/3cc404f1c0a0a5203a773c8a967f0c5a.poster.avif?t=1745482095\" width=575 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756470/extras/3cc404f1c0a0a5203a773c8a967f0c5a.webm?t=1745482095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
